---++ Work plan

   * *Game identification*
      1 Review existing literature on games with a purpose (based on the list linked above)
      1 Search for open source implementation of games
      1 Classify them according to the type of game, number of player, action performed by the user, possible injection of annotation tasks
      1 Discuss which game types are most suitable for our purposes
   * *Game development*
      1 Discuss the game architecture
      1 Inject the annotation data into a game setting
      1 Try the game in a pilot study
   * *Game deployment*
      1 Carry out a game-based annotation study
      1 Extract the annotated data from the game
      1 Analyze the annotated data
      1 Compare different paradigms of annotating data

